        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'I\\'ve decided to start writing here to keep track of things. Perhaps text can better preserve the feelings I want to remember, and the words I didn\\'t know how to express at the time.'}"
    },
    {
